            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Very nice improvement, and so simple!\r\n\r\nOn the removing of code duplication between `flask run` and `app.run()`, I would be super happy if we can also expose the CLI through `app.run()`, along the lines of my PR #2781. So I think I would favor the reverse approach, which is to re-implement `app.run()` to use the `flask run` and CLI logic."
